  <rules>
    <rule id="14d5-906e-8b51-b570" name="Bagpipes" hidden="false">
      <description>Units in this Formation may re-roll a faileed attempt to Rally from Pinned Down as long as their Unit Leader is within 4&quot;/10cm of a Churchill (75mm), Churchill 6pdr), or Churchill (Late 75mm) Tank team that is not Bailed Out.

You may also take the 6th Guards Tank Brigade Title card in your force.</description>
    </rule>
