    </profile>
  </profiles>
  <rules>
    <rule id="9d1f-d912-15c7-57ad" name="AVRE Assault Bridge" hidden="false">
      <description>While this card is face up the Unit Leader cannot Shoot or Assault.

You may deploy this card at the end of any movement steo, placing it face down completely within 4&quot;/10cm of the Unit Leader. This card becomes a bridge that can be used to cross a seawall, creek, stream, or river covered by this card at Tactical or Terrain Dash speed.</description>
    </rule>
  </rules>
